        </comment>
      </geography>
      <technology technologyLevel="3">
        <comment>
          <text xml:lang="en" index="0">This dataset corresponds to a mix of different brick production technologies (different firing fuels) in Austria, Germany and Switzerland.</text>
        </comment>
      </technology>
